Description_lang: The Jailer binds his current target in chains, inflicting $369808s1 Physical damage every $t1 sec for $d and growing in intensity over time.The target is chained to the nearest  $s6 allies, who suffer any Physical damage taken by the primary target until their chains are broken. Moving $s5 yards from the primary target breaks a chain and triggers Chain Breaker.
AuraDescription_lang: $369808s1 Physical damage taken every $t1 sec.All Physical damage taken is mirrored to linked allies.
